<p class="note-body">Corporation of Foreign Bondholders Act, 1933, see <uscode edition="1999" section="77mm" title="15">section 77mm of this title</uscode>.</p>
<p class="note-body">Investment Advisers Act of 1940, see section 80b–20 of this title.</p>
<p class="note-body">Investment Company Act of 1940, see section 80a–51 of this title.</p>
<p class="note-body">Public Utility Holding Company Act of 1935, see <uscode edition="1999" section="79" title="15">section 79 of this title</uscode>.</p>
<p class="note-body">Securities Act of 1933, see <uscode edition="1999" section="77a" title="15">section 77a of this title</uscode>.</p>
<p class="note-body">Securities Investor Protection Act of 1970, see <uscode edition="1999" section="78aaa" title="15">section 78aaa et seq. of this title</uscode>.</p>
<p class="note-body">Trust Indenture Act of 1939, see <uscode edition="1999" section="77aaa" title="15">section 77aaa of this title</uscode>.</p>
<!-- field-end:crossreference-note -->
<!-- field-end:notes -->
