<h4 class="note-head">Act Referred to in Other Sections</h4>
<!-- field-end:secref -->
<!-- field-start:sectionreferredto -->
<p class="note-body">The Foreign Corrupt Practices Act of 1977 [see Short Title of 1977 Amendment note above] is referred to in title 7 <uscode edition="1999" section="12a" title="22">section 12a, title 22</uscode> section 2197.</p>
