<p class="note-body">Applications for unlisted trading privileges deemed filed and approved, see section 78<em>l</em>–1 of this title.</p>
<p class="note-body">Cooperative association defined under Agricultural Marketing Act, as amended, see <uscode edition="1999" section="1141j" title="12">section 1141j of Title 12</uscode>, Banks and Banking.</p>
<p class="note-body">Effective date, see sections 78hh and 78hh–1 of this title.</p>
<!-- PDFPage:218 --><p class="note-body">Issue of securities by electric utility company engaged in interstate commerce, see <uscode edition="1999" section="824c" title="16">section 824c of Title 16</uscode>, Conservation.</p>
