<p class="note-body">Effective date, see <uscode edition="1999" section="78hh" title="15">section 78hh of this title</uscode>.</p>
<p class="note-body">Persons owning securities or affiliated with closed-end company, duties and liabilities of, see section 80a–29 of this title.</p>
