<p class="note-body">Securities with unlisted trading privileges, exemption from the operation of this section, see section 78<em>l</em> of this title.</p>
<p class="note-body">Short sales in contravention of rules and regulations of Commission, see <uscode edition="1999" section="78j" title="15">section 78j of this title</uscode>.</p>
<!-- field-end:crossreference-note -->
