<p class="note-body">Subsecs. (f), (g). <plaw congress="105" isprivate="false" number="353">Pub. L. 105–353,</plaw> §301(b)(13)(B), redesignated subsec. (g) as (f).</p>
<p class="note-body">Subsec. (g)(2)(B)(i). <plaw congress="105" isprivate="false" number="353">Pub. L. 105–353,</plaw> §301(b)(13)(A), substituted “subparagraph (A)” for “paragraph (1)”.</p>
<p class="note-body"><b>1995</b>—Subsec. (g). <plaw congress="104" isprivate="false" number="67">Pub. L. 104–67,</plaw> §201(a), added subsec. (g).</p>
